Pimville will be brought to a standstill. That's the warning from residents who met on Tuesday over the killing of a resident. eNCA's Lindokuhle Xulu reports. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Pimville will be brought to a standstill. That's the warning from residents who met on Tuesday over the killing of a resident. Kgomotso Diale was gunned down while others were injured. It's believed a group of gunmen, believed to be foreigners from a nearby informal settlement, are behind the shooting. * eNCA's Lindokuhle Xulu reports.